contentrichtext.text: '''MW''' or '''mW''' may refer to: ==Companies== *Logo of [[Men's Wearhouse]], a men's dress apparel retailer *[[Merriam-Webster]], an American publisher of dictionaries etc. *[[Mountain West Conference]], an American collegiate sports conference *[[Maya Island Air]] (IATA airline designator) ==Entertainment== *[[MW (manga)|''MW'' (manga)]], a manga series by Osamu Tezuka *Logo of [[Miss World]], an international beauty pageant *[[Museums and the Web]], an international conference series *[[MW (film)|''MW'' (film)]], a 2009 Japanese film *[[Mythic Warriors]] cartoon series ===Games=== *[[Muddy Waters (online game)|''Muddy Waters'' (online game)]], a text-based online role-playing game *''[[Need for Speed: Most Wanted (disambiguation)|Need for Speed: Most Wanted]]'', two racing video games ==Places== *[[Malawi]], ISO 3166-1 country code **[[.mw]], the country code top level domain (ccTLD) for Malawi *The [[Midwestern United States]] (a region) ==Science== *[[Megawatt]], (MW) a unit of power *[[Milliwatt]], (mW) one thousandth of a watt *Molecular weight, a former term for [[molecular mass]] *[[Microwave]], a type electromagnetic wave *'''M<sub>w</sub>''' may refer to: ** [[Moment magnitude scale]], a measure of earthquake size ** [[Weight average molecular weight]] ==Other== *[[Master of Wine]], a wine expertise qualification *[[Medium wave]], a radio band *[[Maintenance_window]], A window of time where some sort of Maintenance is performed. ==See also== *[[MWI (disambiguation)]] *[[MW1 (disambiguation)]] *[[MWA (disambiguation)]] {{disambiguation}}
